Welcome to the Simulation workspace, here's how to get started.
Electronics Cooling: Adjust the design of a power supply enclosure to reduce board component temperatures to below their temperature thresholds. Do now.
Injection Molding Simulation: Modify a hedge trimmer design to improve the fill pattern and part quality. Do now.
Modal Frequencies: Adjust a tuning fork to hit the desired musical pitch. Do now.
Nonlinear Static Stress: Load a simply-supported beam beyond its yield strength, to the verge of collapse. Do now.
Dynamic Event Simulation: Insert a snapfit connector or roll sheet metal. See how they deform over time. Do now.
Quasi-static Event Simulation: Push it, squeeze it, load it. See the stresses and large deformations, due to heavy loads applied at a constant rate. Do now.
Structural Buckling: Simulate a compressive load on a plastic table. Do now.
Shape Optimization: Optimize a robot gripper arm to produce a much lighter version. Do now.
Static Stress: Simulate a connecting rod with a 3,600 pound tensile load. Do now.
Thermal: Compare temperature profiles from two different radiator designs. Do now.
Thermal Stress: Simulate stress in a brake rotor caused by uneven heating. Do now.
Electronics Cooling: Simulate the temperature. Is the design likely to overheat given natural air convection or a fan? Watch now
Injection Molding Simulation: Inject plastic. How well does it fill and how much will it warp? Watch now.
Modal Frequencies: Shake it. Does the design vibrate apart? Watch now.
Nonlinear Static Stress: Large deformations, nonlinear materials, and load or contact changes? Watch now.
Dynamic Event Simulation: Move it, hit it. Does it withstand rapidly changing time-dependent loads and constraints? Watch now
Quasi-static Event Simulation: Push it, squeeze it, load it. How does it respond to heavy loads applied at a constant rate? Watch now
Structural Buckling: Compress. Does the part or assembly collapse? Watch now.
Shape Optimization: Want to make your part lighter without compromising strength or stiffness? Watch now.
Static Stress: Push, pull or twist. Does the design bend...or break? Watch now.
Thermal: Apply heat. Does the temperature get too high? Watch now.
Thermal Stress: Apply heat unevenly. How much does it bend or warp? Watch now.
